---
title: Super Quick Beef and Pea Rogan Josh with Bulgur and Yoghurt
description: Ready in just 15 minutes, our Super Quick Beef and Pea Rogan Josh is fully delicious. Though rogan josh is traditionally made with lamb, this staple Kashmiri dish works just as well with beef or even goat! The sauce is aromatic and rich, spiced with ground coriander, cumin, paprika and turmeric.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W44_UK_UQ25514-4_MAIN_low-f32447dc.jpg
